deploy:


把下载的 geckodriver-v0.16.1-linux64.tar.gz 释放到/bin下



then you extract the file: tar -xvzf geckodriver*
now we make the driver executable: chmod +x geckodriver
In order for tools to use the driver you will need to add the driver to your path: export PATH=$PATH:/path-to-extracted-file/geckodriver

sudo update -y
sudo dist-upgrade -y
sudo apt-get install iceweasel
sudo pip install selenium

pip install pyvirtualdisplay selenium
apt-get install xvfb



